  <h2 id="claims-and-service">Claims and Service</h2>

  <h3>Filing Claims</h3>
  <p>
    SafetyWing handles claims through their online portal. The process is straightforward:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Submission:</strong> Upload receipts and documentation online or via email</li>
    <li><strong>Required documents:</strong> Itemized bills, proof of payment, medical reports</li>
    <li><strong>Processing time:</strong> 10-30 business days typical</li>
    <li><strong>Payment:</strong> Direct deposit, PayPal, or check</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Direct Billing Process</h3>
  <p>
    For hospitalizations over $1,000:
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li>Call the 24/7 assistance line before admission if possible</li>
    <li>Provide your policy information to the hospital</li>
    <li>SafetyWing coordinates guarantee of payment</li>
    <li>Hospital bills SafetyWing directly</li>
  </ol>
  <p>
    For outpatient care and smaller claims, you'll typically pay upfront and submit for reimbursement.
  </p>

